Class Car

java.lang.Object
app.Car
public class Car extends Object
The Car class represents a vehicle with details such as year, make, model, odometer reading, and engine size.

    • Car

      public Car(int year, String make, String model, int odometer, double engineLiters)
      Constructor with parameters to initialize the Car object.
      Parameters:
      year - The manufacturing year of the car.
      make - The brand of the car.
      model - The model of the car.
      odometer - The current mileage of the car.
      engineLiters - The engine size in liters.
